Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:55.15,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつもはじまりはこのOne step
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:58.65,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}とこまでも続くこのOne step
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:03.70,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}遠く遠く　見たことのない景色へ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:09.70,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}One step One step One step
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:20.15,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}立ち止まれば　簡単に終りが来るけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:26.10,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}君の足跡は　無駄にしたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:29.85,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}ぼやけた未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:33.97,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}振り切って走り出す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:52.55,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}この手を引いた好奇心と君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:21:00.51,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}柔らかい声が　瞳が　また「一歩」を生む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:05.18,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつもはじまりはこのOne step
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:08.63,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}とこまでも続くこのOne step
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:13.27,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}遠く遠く　見たことのない景色へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.92,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}一緒に歩んでいこう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:19.15,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}自分の殻を脱いでOne step
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:22.67,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}追い求めた光へOne step
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:27.74,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}そうだ今日も　まだ知らない世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:33.70,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}One step One step One step
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:29.28,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}回家路上同行的腳步聲亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:35.58,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}那天和今天的道路太過不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:46.00,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}視線變得模糊 喉嚨彷彿被堵住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:50.04,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}深吸一口氣又緩緩呼出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:55.15,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}One step總是一切的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:58.65,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}One step通往無限的遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:03.70,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}邁向遙遠的從未見過的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:09.70,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}One step One step One step
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:20.15,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}停下腳步 終結就會輕易到來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:26.10,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}但我不願辜負你的足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:29.85,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}甩開模糊的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.03,0:20:33.97,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}向前奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:52.55,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}好奇心和你一起牽著我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:21:00.51,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}溫柔的聲音和眼眸又醞釀出新的「一步」
