Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:08.63,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}One step通往無限的遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:13.27,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}邁向遙遠的從未見過的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.92,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}讓我們一起前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:19.15,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}卸下自己的硬殼踏出One step
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:22.67,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}朝著追求的光芒踏出One step
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:27.74,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}今天也要邁向未知的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:33.70,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}One step One step One step
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,staff1,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,特別暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.59,0:00:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你們可得好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,因為接下來要有一段時間接觸不到溫暖的地面了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.55,0:00:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在南極也這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.73,0:00:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,準備啟航！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就快了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.65,0:00:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是終於
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,船離開了陸地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我並不知道這趟旅行會有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.99,0:00:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,休了學 也不參加考試 還會影響高考
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是現在的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.15,0:01:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,已經不是一步也邁不出的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不是想要做些什麼卻還什麼也做不到的16歲和17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,滿眼都是大海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是當然的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,世界真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.38,0:01:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 我要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,都看過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,來 茄子
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（OP）
